OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Jennifer
OL,7,FMawby
OL,9,FAir conditioning scams have increased
OL,10,Fby 700%, according to data exclusively
OL,11,Fgiven to ITV News by the UK's fraud
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,FFake products and websites are
OL,15,Ftricking shoppers into getting a cool
OL,16,Fdeal that is often too good to be true.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
