OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FExperts say criminals are taking
OL,7,Fadvantage of hot and tired parents
OL,8,Fduring the school holidays, who are
OL,9,Foften looking for something quick and
OL,10,Fon a budget.
OL,12,FMany air con units sold on legitimate
OL,13,Fretailers are also out of stock due to
OL,14,Frecent heatwaves, making fake online
OL,15,Fdeals all the more appealing.
OL,17,FWhat do air conditioning scams look
OL,18,Flike?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
