CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FSuperintendent Amanda Wolf works for
OL,7,FCity of London Police's Head of Report
OL,8,FFraud Operations, who provide a
OL,9,Fnational reporting service for cyber
OL,10,Fcrime and fraud in England, Wales and
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,FShe said they have seen a "real
OL,14,Fincrease" in air con scams,
OL,15,Fparticularly in May and June, due to
OL,16,Fthe heatwaves in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FSuperintendent Wolf said it is "even
OL,7,Fharder now" for people to recognise
OL,8,Ffake adverts and websites as scammers
OL,9,Fare using artificial intelligence to
OL,10,Ftarget victims.
OL,12,FScams can appear as emails with links
OL,13,Fto air conditioning deals, which steal
OL,14,Fthe user's personal data when they
OL,15,Fclick on them. These are known as
OL,16,Fphishing scams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
