CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FSecurity expert Tatyana Shishkova said
OL,7,Ffake products are also being sold on
OL,8,Ffake websites designed to mimic
OL,9,Flegitimate retailers who are actually
OL,10,Fsold out of air con units.
OL,12,FCustomers buy the air con thinking
OL,13,Fthey are getting a good deal, but
OL,14,Ftheir personal information is stolen
OL,15,Fand they are at risk of eing scammed
OL,16,Fout of more money than the cost of the
OL,17,Fproduct.
OL,19,FSome may even receive a fake tracking
OL,20,Femail implying their order is
OL,21,Fauthentic when it is not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
