OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FSuperintendent Wolf said: "You order
OL,7,Fsomething and it never arrives because
OL,8,Fit's a fake setup, it's a copied
OL,9,Fwebsite.
OL,11,F"It's a completely new entity that can
OL,12,Fbe set up in five minutes with a
OL,13,Fwebsite template."
OL,15,FWhat can you do to avoid being scammed?
OL,17,FThe police advise people to "stop,
OL,18,Fthink, check" before clicking on email
OL,19,Flinks and shopping online, as scams
OL,20,Fcan be difficult to spot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,F"Don't click on the links, look at
OL,7,Fwhere the emails come from because
OL,8,Fquite often at first glance it will
OL,9,Fseem to be from someone genuine,"
OL,10,FSuperintendent Wolf said.
OL,12,F"Thirty seconds could be the
OL,13,Fdifference between you actually having
OL,14,Fthe money to get an aircon unit when
OL,15,Fthey are available, to actually never
OL,16,Fbeing able to afford to buy one, which
OL,17,Fis just awful when you're so in need
OL,18,Fof one too."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
