OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FSuperintendent Wolf emphasised the
OL,7,Fimportance of checking tiny details,
OL,8,Fsuch as the website URLs and email
OL,9,Faddresses, to ensure there are no
OL,10,Ftypos and everything looks legitimate.
OL,12,FCustomers are also advised to shop on
OL,13,Flegitimate websites, and if in doubt
OL,14,Fring the company to check they are
OL,15,Freal.
OL,17,FThey should also search for the
OL,18,Fcompany on a web browser and try to
OL,19,Fread customer reviews before
OL,20,Fpurchasing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
