OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FAre any other scams on the rise?
OL,8,FPolice have also warned that text
OL,9,Fscams are rife at the moment, with
OL,10,Fcriminals taking advantage of the hot
OL,11,Fweather to con people out of money.
OL,13,FMany people receive fake messages,
OL,14,Fsupposedly from relatives in danger,
OL,15,Fasking for financial help.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
