OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784846882
OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FThe text might say something like, "Hi
OL,7,FMum I'm really hot and I think I'm
OL,8,Fgoing to pass out. The hospital says I
OL,9,Fneed a fan, I can't afford one," City
OL,10,Fof London Police's fraud experts
OL,11,Fexplained.
OL,13,FPhone numbers often look real but they
OL,14,Fare not, the experts said.
OL,16,FPolice are urging people to stay
OL,17,Fvigilant by ringing the relative or
OL,18,Fsomeone who knows them to check their
OL,19,Fclaims are true before following
OL,20,Fthrough with any request.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
