OL,3,CHow can you avoid air conditioning
OL,4,Cscams?
OL,6,FThey can also stop traffic from
OL,7,Fcertain websites coming through to
OL,8,Fpeople via their internet service
OL,9,Fproviders as well.
OL,11,FConsumers are urged to report email
OL,12,Fscams to The National Cyber Security
OL,13,FCentre by emailing
OL,14,Freport@phishing.gov.uk so they can
OL,15,Ftake down the sites.
OL,17,FIf you've been affected by a scam,
OL,18,Fcontact Report Fraud's Victim Support
OL,19,Fline on 0808 1689 111.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
